---
import profil3 from '../assets/profil3.jpeg';
---
<div class="magazine-page h-full">
  <div class="page-content h-full">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-2">Nos Services</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-primary"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 flex-grow">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-palette"><circle cx="13.5" cy="6.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="10.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="7.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="6.5" cy="12.5" r="2.5"/><path d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12s4.5 10 10 10c.9 0 1.6-.7 1.6-1.6 0-.4-.2-.8-.5-1.1s-.5-.8-.5-1.2c0-.9.7-1.6 1.6-1.6H19c2.2 0 4-1.8 4-4 0-5.5-4.5-10-10-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-2">Création graphique</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Stratégie de communication adaptée à votre identité et vos objectifs pour raconter votre histoire avec authenticité.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-layout"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-2">Création de Site Web</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Sites web modernes et responsifs, conçus pour refléter votre univers et convertir vos visiteurs en clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-fingerprint"><path d="M2 12a10 10 0 0 1 13-9.54"/><path d="M7 20a10 10 0 0 1 0-16"/><path d="M12 20a10 10 0 0 1 0-16"/><path d="M17 20a10 10 0 0 1 0-16"/><path d="M22 12a10 10 0 0 0-13-9.54"/><path d="M2 12v.01"/><path d="M7 21v.01"/><path d="M12 21v.01"/><path d="M17 21v.01"/><path d="M22 12v.01"/><path d="M7 13a5 5 0 0 1 5-5"/><path d="M7 17a10 10 0 0 1 10-10"/><path d="M7 21a15 15 0 0 1 15-15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-2">Identité Visuelle</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Création d'une identité visuelle cohérente et distinctive : logo, charte graphique, branding complet.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-dark text-light rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex gap-6 items-center">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-highlight/20">
        <img src={profil3.src} alt="Aurélie Magontier" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold text-highlight mb-2">Ma Philosophie</h3>
        <p class="text-xs italic leading-relaxed opacity-90">
          "Je crois que chaque entreprise porte une histoire unique. Mon rôle est de vous aider à la transmettre avec clarté, authenticité et élégance."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
